---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../site.config';

const baw = SITE.projects[0];
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Bookmark All Windows" theme="baw">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-10 relative z-10">
    <h1 class="text-[2rem] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 pb-4 border-b border-[#2e2e3a]">
      <strong class="text-slate-300">Bookmark All Windows</strong> - Browser Extension<br />
      Last Updated: January 3, 2026
    </p>

    <div class="bg-[#202027] border border-[#2e2e3a] rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-[var(--color-accent)] text-xl font-semibold mt-0 mb-3">🔒 TL;DR</h2>
      <p class="mb-2 text-slate-300">
        <strong>We don't collect, store, or transmit any of your data. Period.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-0">
        The extension works entirely offline within your browser. Your browsing data never leaves your device.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <div class="bg-emerald-950/40 border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <strong class="text-emerald-400">We collect absolutely NO information.</strong>
    </div>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The "Bookmark All Windows" extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information or browsing
      data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. How the Extension Works</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">The extension operates entirely within your browser:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-slate-300">Tab Information</strong>: The extension reads tab URLs and titles only when you
        click the bookmark button. This information is used solely to create bookmarks and is never stored or
        transmitted anywhere.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-slate-300">Bookmarks</strong>: Bookmarks are created using your browser's built-in bookmark
        system. They are stored locally by your browser, not by the extension.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-slate-300">No External Communication</strong>: The extension does not connect to any
        external servers, APIs, or services.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Browser Permissions</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">The extension requires the following permissions:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-slate-300">tabs</strong>: Required to read the URLs and titles of your open tabs.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-slate-300">bookmarks</strong>: Required to create bookmark folders and save bookmarks to
        your browser.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      These permissions are used exclusively for the extension's core functionality. No data accessed through these
      permissions is collected, stored, or shared.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Storage</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The extension does not store any data. All bookmarks are stored by your browser's native bookmark system, which
      you have full control over.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The extension does not use any third-party services, analytics, tracking, or advertising.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Since we don't collect any data, there is no data to share. We do not sell, trade, or transfer any information to
      third parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The extension does not collect any information from anyone, including children under 13 years of age.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated
      revision date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">9. Open Source</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This extension is open source. You can review the complete source code on <a
        href={baw.repoUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">GitHub</a
      > to verify our privacy practices.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions, please open an issue on our <a
        href={baw.repoUrl}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">GitHub repository</a
      >.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-[#2e2e3a] text-center text-slate-500">
      <p>{SITE.author.copyright}</p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        <a href="/bookmark-all-windows/terms" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">Terms of Use</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
